data.title: Corey Manning Franklin Tickets, Box Seats Sep 14, 2024
data.meta_description: Corey Manning is coming to Box Seats in Franklin on Sep 14, 2024. Find tickets and get exclusive show information, all at Bandsintown.
data.text:
Currently streaming on Amazon Prime, he has headlined The Apollo Theater and appeared on Family Feud. Don't miss a great night of comedy with Comedian By Night and Superhero By Day, Corey Manning.

A native of Durham, NC, Corey began working on his comedic skills at the age of 6. His talent landed him in principals' offices at Hope Valley Elementary, Githen's Junior High and Durham High School. Since graduating from North Carolina Central University, he has performed in Jamie Foxx's Laffapalooza, and all over the world; east coast, west coast, and as far as the Middle East and Taiwan. He has toured with some of the best comedians in the world; Moâ€™Nique, Rodney Perry, Talent, Damon Wayans, Bill Bellamy, Bobby Collins, Tracy Morgan, Robert Kelly, Earthquake, Chris Thomas, Arnez J., Tommy Davidson, Lavell Crawford, Adele Givens, Kevin Knox, Bruce Bruce, Sheryl Underwood, and John Witherspoon. Just to name a few. Ok, it's more than a few.

Corey Manning is "a comedian who is really making a name for himself nationally." ~ Bob Sumner, Producer for Laff Mobb and Russell Simmon's Def Comedy Jam.
